text: Endurance Tire changing - what is true?

answer_options.answer_text: If I elect to change to wet tires, I may do so during the driver change
'Wheel Guns' driven from compressed air/gas are prohibited
For changing tires, up to four team members are allowed to work on the car
If I elect to change to dry tires, the time for changing is not included in my endurance time

answers.answer_text: If I elect to change to wet tires, I may do so during the driver change
